## Definitions

- **"Software"** means the Classly source code, documentation, and associated files
  in this repository.
- **"You"** means the individual or legal entity exercising the rights granted by
  this License.
- **"Non-Commercial Use"** means use that is not primarily intended for or directed
  toward commercial advantage or monetary compensation.
- **"Commercial Use"** means any use primarily intended for or directed toward
  commercial advantage, monetary compensation, or revenue generation.
- **"For-Profit Organization"** means any entity organized or operated with the
  primary purpose of generating profit for its owners, shareholders, or members.
- **"Non-Profit Organization"** means any entity organized and operated exclusively
  for charitable, educational, religious, or scientific purposes, where no part of
  the net earnings benefits any private shareholder or individual.
- **"Educational Institution"** means any accredited school, college, university,
  or other educational organization.
- **"Self-Hosting"** means deploying and operating the Software on infrastructure
  that You own or control, solely for Your own use or the use of Your organization.

